# No Emojis

Never use pictographic emojis (the kind found on an iOS keyboard) anywhere in the codebase - UI strings, console logs, comments, or error messages.

## What to avoid

Unicode emoji characters like: 🎉 📊 ⚠️ ✅ 🔗 💡 🎵 ⏳ 👥 🌐 📥 📤 🔧 🚀 ✨ 🔥 etc.

## What's fine to use

- Standard Unicode glyphs/symbols: `×`, `✕`, `←`, `→`, `✓`, `✗`, `▼`, `•`
- Icon libraries: FontAwesome, Lucide, Heroicons, or any SVG icon component
- Plain text labels
